snippet.title: Best VGM 1037 - Donkey Kong Country Returns - Palm Tree Groove
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1400 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bR4AB3xNT0c

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Donkey Kong Country Returns (2010)
Palm Tree Groove
Kenji Yamamoto
